text:
I guess I would print out the variable inside the post inside a hidden div inside the post content (not sure if you can do that though)

&lt;div class="hidden" id="hubl-var"&gt;
{{ hubl.var }}
&lt;/div&gt;

And then in the listing page use Jquery to grab it and do what you need 
var hubl_var = $('#hubl-var').text()
